<topic id='element_treatment_start_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: TREATMENT START DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE) - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
    <dl>
      <dlentry>
        <dt>Format / Length</dt>
        <dd>an10 CCYY-MM-DD</dd>
      </dlentry>
    </dl>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_treatment_start_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">TREATMENT START DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the same as data element 
    <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_treatment_start_date__cancer_">TREATMENT START DATE (CANCER)</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_treatment_start_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">TREATMENT START DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the 
    <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_treatment_start_date__cancer_">TREATMENT START DATE (CANCER)</xref>
 where the treatment is being undertaken as part of a 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_cancer_treatment_period">Cancer Treatment Period</xref>
 and where the 
    <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_cancer_treatment_modality">CANCER TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>
 is National Code 
    <i>
'
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_teletherapy">Teletherapy</xref>
'    </i>
 or 
    <i>
'
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_brachytherapy">Brachytherapy</xref>
'.    </i>
  </p>
  <p>
      <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_treatment_start_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">TREATMENT START DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the date that treatment for a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
's condition using a 
    <xref outputclass="attribute"
            keyref="attribute_radiotherapy_treatment_modality">RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT MODALITY</xref>
 started.  </p>
  <p>
For the 
    <xref outputclass="dataSet" keyref="dataset_radiotherapy_data_set">Radiotherapy Data Set</xref>
, 
    <xref outputclass="element"
            keyref="element_treatment_start_date__radiotherapy_treatment_episode_">TREATMENT START DATE (RADIOTHERAPY TREATMENT EPISODE)</xref>
 is the date the first 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_fraction">Fraction</xref>
 of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_radiotherapy">Radiotherapy</xref>
 was given to the 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 in the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_radiotherapy_episode">Radiotherapy Episode</xref>
.  </p>


  </body>
